---
import Logo from "../components/logo.astro";
import { Sprite } from "astro-icon";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <title>Valink Solutions</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.bunny.net" />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.bunny.net/css?family=arvo:400,400i,700,700i"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body
    class="relative flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen w-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-purple-800 text-white p-2 md:p-4 overflow-x-hidden"
  >
    <div class="absolute w-full h-full bg-slate-900 opacity-60 -z-50"></div>
    <div class="max-w-sm md:max-w-prose flex flex-col gap-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 lg:gap-3">
        <div class="h-36 md:h-40 text-center">
          <Logo />
        </div>
        <h1
          class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold text-center font-arvo"
          style="letter-spacing: 0.16em;"
        >
          Creating Powerful & Effecient Software Solutions
        </h1>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 p-4 bg-opacity-25 bg-slate-900 rounded">
        <h1
          class="text-2xl font-black font-arvo border-l-4 text-left pl-3 border-purple-500"
        >
          About Us
        </h1>
        <p class="max-w-sm md:max-w-prose tracking-wide">
          Based in Ontario, Canada, Valink Solutions is a software development firm that excels in backend development.
          With a strong focus on innovation and client satisfaction, our team of skilled developers creates bespoke software solutions tailored to each client's unique needs.
          But our passion doesn't stop there; we also dedicate our time and expertise to crafting software for personal use and projects aimed at bettering communities.
        </p>
        <p class="max-w-sm md:max-w-prose tracking-wide">
          One of our noteworthy community-focused initiatives is <a class="font-bold hover:text-purple-500" href="http://github.com/Valink-Solutions/ChunkVault-Lite" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ChunkVault</a>, a Minecraft world backup system that ensures the seamless preservation of players' virtual worlds.
          This project is complemented by Teller, a user-friendly client that interfaces with ChunkVault to provide an intuitive experience for players.
          Although both projects are currently in the early proof-of-concept stages, our commitment to developing technologies that resonate with users is unwavering.
        </p>
        <p class="max-w-sm md:max-w-prose tracking-wide">
          At Valink Solutions, our goal is not only to build software that meets the demands of today's ever-evolving digital landscape but also to create solutions that enrich the lives of those who use them.
          By embracing challenges and pushing the boundaries of what's possible, we continue to grow and innovate, ensuring that our clients, our users, and our communities all reap the benefits of our expertise.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 p-4 bg-opacity-25 bg-slate-900 rounded">
        <h1
          class="text-2xl font-black font-arvo border-l-4 text-left pl-3 border-purple-500"
        >
          Get In Touch
        </h1>
        <div
          class="flex flex-row justify-around bg-opacity-50 bg-slate-900 p-4 rounded"
        >
          <Sprite.Provider>
            <a
              href="https://twitter.com/valink_io"
              target="_blank"
              class="text-2xl font-bold hover:text-purple-500"
            >
              <Sprite pack="mdi" name="twitter-box" size="60px" />
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://facebook.com/valinksolutions"
              target="_blank"
              class="text-2xl font-bold hover:text-purple-500"
            >
              <Sprite pack="mdi" name="facebook-box" size="60px" />
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://www.instagram.com/valink.io/"
              target="_blank"
              class="text-2xl font-bold hover:text-purple-500"
            >
              <Sprite pack="mdi" name="instagram" size="60px" />
            </a>
            <a
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/valink-solutions/"
              target="_blank"
              class="text-2xl font-bold hover:text-purple-500"
            >
              <Sprite pack="mdi" name="linkedin-box" size="60px" />
            </a>
            <a
              href="mailto:jake@valink.io"
              target="_blank"
              class="text-2xl font-bold hover:text-purple-500"
            >
              <Sprite pack="mdi" name="email" size="60px" />
            </a>
          </Sprite.Provider>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
